description:
Loma Linda University and Hospital is a flagship institution within the Seventh Day Adventist Church. Since launching, they have both made a real impact in the field of health care, in the US and further afield. The beginnings of this school are quite remarkable and date back to 1905, representing great foresight by our early pioneers. Over the years, many missionaries have completed their studies at this school, and have taken their learnings from the message of Jesus around the world with them.

To find out more information about Loma Linda visit our website to read our extended article.
